&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This role will be&amp;nbsp;hybrid, requiring 2-3&amp;nbsp;days a&amp;nbsp;week&amp;nbsp;at our office in Concord, MA.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
